            Latest mobile games, reviews, tips, and strategies for iOS and Android gaming experiences.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">üñ•Ô∏è</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">PC Gaming</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Hardware reviews, game performance analysis, and guides for building the ultimate gaming PC.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
